<p style="margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%"><img src= ![ciab-logo](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/1682855/51850975-ea4e3480-22f0-11e9-9128-d945e1e2a9ab.png?classes=float-left)name="Image1" align="left" width="270" height="200" border="0"/>
The
CIAB Remote Desktop System  is a <b>clientless</b> remote desktop
system.  It's called &quot;<i>clientless</i>&quot; because no plugins
or client software are required!   
</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%">  
</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 0in; line-height: 100%">Thanks to HTML5,
once the CIAB Remote Desktop System is installed on a Server/VM/Cloud
instance, all you need to access your desktop(s) is an HTML5 capable
web browser!  
</p>
